SQL_STMT_U.val:
select hr_x_msgtype, hr_x_ep_in_out, hr_x_epmsgseqnum, er_i_clordid from (select t.hr_x_msgtype, t.hr_x_ep_in_out, t.hr_x_epmsgseqnum, er.er_i_clordid from hr_header t left outer join er_i_executionreport er on er.er_i_x_epmsgseqnum = hr_x_epmsgseqnum where t.hr_x_procesid=~1 and t.hr_x_berichtverwerkt=0 and t.hr_x_ep_in_out='I'
order by t.hr_x_procesid, t.hr_x_berichtverwerkt, t.hr_x_ep_in_out, t.hr_x_priority, t.hr_x_datetimein, t.hr_x_epmsgseqnum ) where rownum <= 1
